'''AirPods Max'''是[[蘋果公司|蘋果公司]]于2020年12月15日發售的无线[[蓝牙|蓝牙]][[耳機|头戴式耳机]]。<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=苹果 AirPods Max，传说中的头戴式 ANC 耳机终于面世了|url=https://cn.engadget.com/apple-airpods-max-launc-134206458.html|accessdate=|author=engadget|date=|format=|publisher=|language=|archive-date=2020-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201219112925/https://cn.engadget.com/apple-airpods-max-launc-134206458.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>AirPods Max內置[[Apple_Silicon|Apple H1芯片]]，搭载苹果[[主动降噪|主动降噪]]技术，可以阻挡外界噪音。用户可以通過耳機可以控制音频播放和音量和啟動[[Siri|Siri]] <ref>{{Cite web|title=Apple announces $549 AirPods Max noise-canceling headphones, coming December 15th|url=https://www.theverge.com/2020/12/8/21438042/apple-max-studio-noise-canceling-headphones-price-date|accessdate=2020-12-08|author=Welch|date=2020-12-08|first=Chris|work=The Verge|language=en|archive-date=2020-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201208193833/https://www.theverge.com/2020/12/8/21438042/apple-max-studio-noise-canceling-headphones-price-date|dead-url=no}}</ref> <ref>{{Cite web|title=Apple Announces AirPods Max Over-Ear Headphones With Noise Cancellation, Priced at $549|url=https://www.macrumors.com/2020/12/08/airpods-max/|accessdate=2020-12-08|work=www.macrumors.com|archive-date=2020-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201208160052/https://www.macrumors.com/2020/12/08/airpods-max/|dead-url=no}}</ref> <ref>{{Cite web|title=Apple announces $549 AirPods Max over-ear headphones, preorders today, launch Dec. 15|url=https://www.cnet.com/news/apple-announces-549-airpods-max-over-ear-headphones-preorders-today-launch-dec-15/|accessdate=2020-12-08|author=Sherr|first=Ian|work=CNET|language=en|archive-date=2020-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201208194125/https://www.cnet.com/news/airpods-max-apple-starts-preorders-for-549-over-ear-headphones-arrives-dec-15/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。AirPods Max的电池续航时间为20小时，充电5分钟可以收聽1.5小时。AirPods Max通过[[Lightning接头|Lightning接头]]充电。AirPods Max適用於[[IOS|IOS]] 14.3 、[[IPadOS|IPadOS]] 14.3、[[MacOS_Big_Sur|MacOS Big Sur]] 11.1、[[WatchOS|WatchOS]] 7.2、 [[TvOS|TvOS]] 14.3版本及以上的Apple設備<ref name=":0" />。

